example ex_CombinedAssessmentResults file (formerly Comprehensive Data File)

Source: R/ex_data.R
ex_CombinedAssessmentResults.Rd

MAP assessment results (**post-2015**), in the format provided by web-based MAP. Data provided from NWEA, by request. (Note that this is training data, and these students/student records *are not real*!)
